+- **AT-EXEC-0003**: Run emits AgentExecutionReceipt under `/.a2r/receipts/<run_id>/`.
+- **AT-EXEC-0004**: Deterministic replay reconstructs the same next-node selection.
+- **AT-EXEC-0005**: Missing agent profile is denied.
+
